```java
@PUT
@Path("/{bucket}")
public Response createBucket(...)
```

When the URL is `/test-bucket/src/%E3...png`, the `%` might cause RestAssured to encode it differently. Let me check if RestAssured is double-encoding the `%` - turning `%3E` into `%253E`.

